"{\"uid\": \"nbclosangeles.com-news-national-international-south-african-olympic-runner-oscar-pistorius-released-on-parole-after-nearly-9-years-in-prison-3304346\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"FILE - Oscar Pistorius leaves the High Court in Pretoria, South Africa, on June 14, 2016 during his trail for the murder of girlfriend Reeva Steenkamp.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 4, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electronic_Language_International_Festival\", \"score\": 0.999999999740794, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"FILE\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electronic_Language_International_Festival\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electronic_Language_International_Festival\"}, {\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 22, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.049846262796521e-44, \"text\": \"Oscar Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}, {\"begin\": 34, \"end\": 44, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court_of_South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.6705420619282605, \"rank\": 0.4913306669334134, \"text\": \"High Court\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court_of_South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court_of_South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 48, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9091203961578515e-20, \"text\": \"Pretoria\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\"}, {\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 70, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.829180924774496e-17, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oscar Pistorius is due on Friday, Jan. 5, 2024 to be released from prison on parole to live under strict conditions at a family home after serving nearly nine years of his murder sentence for the shooting death of girlfriend Reeva Steenkamp on Valentine's Day 2013.\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 152, \"end\": 167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.049846262796521e-44, \"text\": \"Oscar Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South African athleteOscar Pistorius\\u00a0has been releasedfrom prison on parole after serving nearly nine years in prison for killing his girlfriend and is now at home, South Africa's Department of Corrections said Friday.\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}, {\"begin\": 584, \"end\": 596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.829180924774496e-17, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The department gave no more details of Pistorius' release.\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 678, \"end\": 687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcement came at around 8:30 a.m., indicating corrections officials had released the world-famous double-amputee Olympic runner from the Atteridgeville Correctional Center in theSouth African capital, Pretoria, in the early hours.\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atteridgeville\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Atteridgeville\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atteridgeville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atteridgeville\"}, {\"begin\": 907, \"end\": 915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9091203961578515e-20, \"text\": \"Pretoria\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stream Los Angeles News for free, 24/7, wherever you are.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 945, \"end\": 956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.396190107855091e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pistorius has served nearly nine years of his 13 years and five months murder sentence for killing girlfriend Reeva Steenkamp on Valentine's Day 2013.\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}, {\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reeva\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was approved for parole in November.\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Serious offenders in South Africa are eligible for parole after serving at least half their sentence.\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1210, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.829180924774496e-17, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Department of Corrections said in a two-sentence statement announcing Pistorius' release that it was \\\"able to confirm that Oscar Pistorius is a parolee, effectively from 5 January 2024.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}, {\"begin\": 1419, \"end\": 1434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.049846262796521e-44, \"text\": \"Oscar Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was admitted into the system of Community Corrections and is now at home.\\\"\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pistorius was expected to initially live at his uncle's mansion in the upscale Waterkloof suburb of Pretoria, and a police van was seen parked outside of that house.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1563, \"end\": 1572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}, {\"begin\": 1642, \"end\": 1652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterkloof\", \"score\": 0.9999980614739488, \"rank\": 1.938529819873362e-06, \"text\": \"Waterkloof\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterkloof\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterkloof\"}, {\"begin\": 1663, \"end\": 1671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9091203961578515e-20, \"text\": \"Pretoria\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Department of Corrections officials had said Pistorius' release time would not be announced in advance and he would not be \\\"paraded\\\" because they hoped to keep him away from the media glare that has trailed him since he shot Steenkamp multiple times through a toilet door at his home in the predawn hours of Feb. 14, 2013.\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1775, \"end\": 1784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will live under strict parole conditions until the remainder of his sentence expires in December 2029.\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2159, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Steenkamp's mother, June Steenkamp, said in a statement earlier Friday that she had accepted Pistorius' parole as part of South African law.\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2254, \"end\": 2263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}, {\"begin\": 2283, \"end\": 2300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"South African law\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Has there been justice for Reeva?\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2331, \"end\": 2336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reeva\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Has Oscar served enough time?\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2342, \"end\": 2347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Academy_Awards\", \"score\": 0.9999792884057861, \"rank\": 2.0707987714655135e-05, \"text\": \"Oscar\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Academy_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Academy_Awards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There can never be justice if your loved one is never coming back, and no amount of time served will bring Reeva back,\\\" June Steenkamp said.\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2475, \"end\": 2480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reeva\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We who remain behind are the ones serving a life sentence.\\\"\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With the release of Oscar Pistorius on parole, my only desire is that I will be allowed to live my last years in peace with my focus remaining on the Reeva Rebecca Steenkamp Foundation, to continue Reeva's legacy.\\\"\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2592, \"end\": 2607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.049846262796521e-44, \"text\": \"Oscar Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}, {\"begin\": 2722, \"end\": 2727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reeva\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\"}, {\"begin\": 2728, \"end\": 2735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Napier\", \"score\": 0.999999992019184, \"rank\": 7.979273037360053e-09, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Napier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Napier\"}, {\"begin\": 2770, \"end\": 2775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reeva\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riva_Bubber\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Department of Corrections has emphasized that the multiple Paralympic champion's release - like every other offender on parole - does not mean that he has served his time.\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of Pistorius' parole conditions include restrictions on when he's allowed to leave his home, a ban on consuming alcohol, and orders that he must attend programs on anger management and on violence against women.\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 3181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2973, \"end\": 2982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will have to perform community service.\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pistorius will also have to regularly meet with parole officials at his home and at correctional services offices and will be subjected to unannounced visits by authorities.\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3399, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3226, \"end\": 3235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is not allowed to leave the Waterkloof district without permission and is banned from speaking to the media until the end of his sentence.\", \"from\": 3400, \"to\": 3541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3431, \"end\": 3441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterkloof\", \"score\": 0.9999980614739488, \"rank\": 1.938529819873362e-06, \"text\": \"Waterkloof\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterkloof\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterkloof\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He could be sent back to jail if he is in breach of any of his parole conditions.\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa does not use tags or bracelets on paroled offenders so Pistorius will not wear any monitoring device, Department of Corrections officials said.\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3625, \"end\": 3637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.829180924774496e-17, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 3693, \"end\": 3702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he will be constantly monitored by a department official and will have to inform the official of any major changes in his life, such as if he wants to get a job or move to another house.\", \"from\": 3782, \"to\": 3972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pistorius has maintained that he shot Steenkamp, a 29-year-old model and law graduate, by mistake.\", \"from\": 3974, \"to\": 4072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3974, \"end\": 3983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He testified that he believed Steenkamp was a dangerous intruder hiding in his bathroom and shot through the door with his licensed 9 mm pistol in self-defense.\", \"from\": 4073, \"to\": 4233, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Prosecutors said he killed his girlfriend intentionally during a late-night argument.\", \"from\": 4235, \"to\": 4320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Steenkamp's family did not oppose his parole application in November, although June Steenkamp said in a victim statement submitted to the parole board that she did not believe Pistorius had been fully rehabilitated and was still lying about the killing.\", \"from\": 4322, \"to\": 4575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4498, \"end\": 4507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before the killing, Pistorius was held up as an inspiring role model after having had both of his legs amputated below the knee as a baby because of a congenital condition.\", \"from\": 4577, \"to\": 4749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4597, \"end\": 4606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He became a champion sprinter on his carbon-fiber running blades and made history by competing at the 2012 London Olympics.\", \"from\": 4750, \"to\": 4873, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But his murder trial destroyed his image.\", \"from\": 4875, \"to\": 4916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was accused of being prone to angry outbursts and acting recklessly with guns, while witnesses testified about various altercations he had with others, including an argument in which he allegedly threatened to break a man's legs.\", \"from\": 4917, \"to\": 5149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pistorius was first\\u00a0convicted of culpable homicide\\u00a0- a charge comparable to manslaughter - and sentenced to five years in prison for killing Steenkamp.\", \"from\": 5151, \"to\": 5302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5151, \"end\": 5160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After appeals by prosecutors, he was ultimately found guilty of murder and had his sentence increased, although that judgment by the Supreme Court of Appeal\\u00a0still did not definitively rule\\u00a0that he knew it was Steenkamp behind the toilet door.\", \"from\": 5303, \"to\": 5545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pistorius was first sent to prison in 2014, was released on house arrest in 2015 during an appeal and was sent back to prison in 2016.\", \"from\": 5547, \"to\": 5681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5547, \"end\": 5556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was initially incarcerated at the maximum security Kgosi Mampuru II Prison in Pretoria but was moved to Atteridgeville early in his sentence because it is better suited to holding disabled prisoners.\", \"from\": 5682, \"to\": 5884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5736, \"end\": 5752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria_Central_Prison\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kgosi Mampuru II\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria_Central_Prison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria_Central_Prison\"}, {\"begin\": 5742, \"end\": 5752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mampuru_II\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mampuru II\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mampuru_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mampuru_II\"}, {\"begin\": 5763, \"end\": 5771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9091203961578515e-20, \"text\": \"Pretoria\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\"}, {\"begin\": 5789, \"end\": 5803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atteridgeville\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Atteridgeville\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atteridgeville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atteridgeville\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reaction to Pistorius' parole has been muted in South Africa, a stark contrast to the first days and months after Steenkamp's killing, which sparked angry protests outside of Pistorius' court hearings calling for him to receive a long prison sentence.\", \"from\": 5886, \"to\": 6137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5898, \"end\": 5907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}, {\"begin\": 5934, \"end\": 5946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.829180924774496e-17, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 6061, \"end\": 6070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no death penalty in South Africa.\", \"from\": 6138, \"to\": 6180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6167, \"end\": 6179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.829180924774496e-17, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He has ticked all the necessary boxes,\\\" said Themba Masango, secretary general of Not In My Name International, a group that campaigns against violence against women.\", \"from\": 6182, \"to\": 6349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6228, \"end\": 6234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euphonik\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Themba\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euphonik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euphonik\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And we can only wish and hope Oscar Pistorius will come out a better human being.\\\"\", \"from\": 6350, \"to\": 6433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6381, \"end\": 6396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.049846262796521e-44, \"text\": \"Oscar Pistorius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Pistorius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We tend to forget that there is a possibility where somebody can be rehabilitated.\\\"\", \"from\": 6435, \"to\": 6519, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"___  Imray reported from Cape Town, South Africa.\", \"from\": 6521, \"to\": 6570, 